java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<ClientCommand>
public enum ClientCommand
extends java.lang.Enum<ClientCommand>

Enumeration of the commands that can be triggered in the ClientView. Each element has an associated ActionCommand value that can be used by ActionListener instances to identify an event source.
